cts it also produces both paving and roofing grades of asphalt and depending on the terminal can manufacture performancegraded asphalts emulsions and cutbacks the retail segment offers various grades of gasoline diesel fuel general merchandise and food and beverage products the company was founded in august  and is headquartered in dallas tx site httpwwwalonusacom shareholders     follow as shareholder governance and management  votos cash and debts  votos consistent profits  votos rating basttercom votos insuficientes energy minerals cvx  chevron corp xom  exxon mobil corp apc  anadarko petroleum corp apa  apache corp chk  chesapeake energy corp xec  cimarex energy co cop  conocophillips cnx  consol energy inc dnr  denbury resources inc dvn  devon energy corp eog  eog resources inc eqt  eqt corp cog  cabot oil  gas corp hal  halliburton co hes  hess corp mro  marathon oil corp mpc  marathon petroleum corp mur  murphy oil corp nfx  newfield exploration co nbl  noble energy inc oxy  occidental petroleum corp psx  phillips  pxd  pioneer natural resources co qep  qep resources inc rrc  range resources corp swn  southwestern energy co tso  tesoro corp vlo  valero energy corp cxo  concho resources inc aav  advantage oil  gas ltd alj  alon usa energy inc ar  antero resources corp arch  arch coal inc bte  baytex energy corp bxe  bellatrix exploration ltd bbg  bill barrett corp bcei  bonanza creek energy inc bp  bp plc crc  california resources corp cpe  callon petroleum co cnq  canadian natural resources ltd cve  cenovus energy inc snp  china petroleum  chemical corp cwei  clayton williams energy inc cld  cloud peak energy inc ceo  cnooc ltd cie  cobalt international energy inc crk  comstock resources inc clr  continental resources inc cpg  crescent point energy corp cvi  cvr energy inc dk  delek us holdings inc ecr  eclipse resources corp ec  ecopetrol sa eca  encana corp egn  energen corp erf  enerplus corp e  eni spa epe  ep energy corp xco  exco resources inc gprk  geo