 motorist on interstate  sustained an injury when debris struck her vehicle according to local reports according to a press release by the company on february  the explosion occurred in the area around the propylene splitter unit although the cause has not yet been determined information on the companys website states that alon usa acquired ownership of the big spring texas refinery in august  when alon israel oil company ltd purchased the us fuels marketing and refining assets of atofina petrochemicals inc fina the refinery has been in service for more than  years and produces fuel products and asphalt for the southwestern united states it was constructed in  by the original owner joshua cosden referencesedit  a b c alon usa energy alj annual sec income statement filing via wikinvest  a b alon usa energy alj annual sec balance sheet filing via wikinvest  delek us alon usa complete merger oilgas journal  july    west texas refinery explodes associated press  february    miracle on i  injured in huge explosion big spring herald  february  check date values in date help  alon usa provides additional information regarding the explosion at the big spring refinery alon usa  february   external linksedit dallas portal companies portal energy portal alon usa corporate site alon executive says change is on the horizon bic magazine interview with jeff morris may  alon israel oil company corporate site retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlealonusaoldid categories companies listed on the new york stock exchangecompanies based in dallashidden categories cs errors datespages using deprecated image syntax navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated chang